How expensive is the wind walk spell? Would it be reasonable for an adventurer to take up wind surfing?
easy for caster adventurers to get- dont even need to be max level
it's a mid tier spell though so you dont get it by dabbling in magic a little bit
I could see some players choosing wizard just for that mid/end game surfing life :ptv-dealwithit:
the flying spell is available a little bit earlier but it's duration is not suited for long distance travel
wind walk - it's designed to be like a mini-game because people were expected to use it for longer adventures
granted it mostly was used to further advance teleportation networks as wizards could also sell runes for people to use to teleport
a rune was just a piece of stone or metal with what was basically GPS coordinates on it that teleport spells would use to determine where to send you
so while wind walking Wizards would use eagle eye to spot interesting locations and mark them with runes as they travelled
